 | rev1Score = PSV：73%<ref name="RPGFvita" />
}}

《圣洁传说》在发售前，和Xbox 360独占游戏《[[失落的奥德赛|失落的奥德赛]]》共为[[日本亚马逊|日本亚马逊]]预定量最高的游戏<ref name="InnocencePre">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/107425/Release_This_Japan_Gets_Heroes_Innocence_SingStar_Hits_UK_PS3s.php | script-title = en:Release This: Japan Gets Heroes, Innocence; SingStar Hits UK PS3s | author = Wesley Eric RE: Candace David Danny Cowen | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2007-12-03 | accessdate = 2015-02-07 | language = en}}</ref>。官方预计本作销量15万，首批出货16万<ref>{{Cite web | date = 2007-12-11 | url = http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/corporate/press/pdf/53-026.pdf | script-title = ja:『テイルズ オブ』シリーズ全世界累計1,000 万本突破！ | publisher = [[Bandai_Namco_Games|Bandai Namco Games]] | format = PDF | accessdate = 2012-09-21 | language = ja | archive-date = 2014-12-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141204225401/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/corporate/press/pdf/53-026.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="HeartsPrepare">{{cite web | url = http://www.cubed3.com/news/11262/1/new-tales-of-hearts-nintendo-ds-and-wii-tidbits.html | script-title = en:New Tales of Hearts Nintendo DS & Wii Tidbits | author = Adam Riley | publisher = Cubed3 | date = 2008-12-08 | accessdate = 2014-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141228190515/http://www.cubed3.com/news/11262/1/new-tales-of-hearts-nintendo-ds-and-wii-tidbits.html | archivedate = 2014-12-28 | deadurl = no | language = en }}</ref>。游戏售周售出10.4万——在当周销量榜上次于《[[Wii_Fit|Wii Fit]]》和《[[马里奥聚会DS|马里奥聚会DS]]》位列第3<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/107571/Wii_Fit_Exercises_Legs_At_Top_Of_Japanese_Charts.php | script-title = en:Wii Fit Exercises Legs At Top Of Japanese Charts | author = Jenkins | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2007-12-13 | accessdate = 2015-02-08 | language = en }}</ref>——但第二周销则跳水到2.8万<ref name="InnocenceDrop">{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2007/12/19/another-week-in-japan-hardware-and-software-numbers-12-10-12-16/ | script-title = en:Another week in Japan: Hardware and software numbers 12/10-12/16 | author = Savino | publisher = [[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | date = 2007-12-17 | accessdate = 2015-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150128142656/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/12/19/another-week-in-japan-hardware-and-software-numbers-12-10-12-16/ | archivedate = 2015-01-28 | deadurl = yes | language = en }}</ref>。《圣洁传说》最终销量约24.6万，超出公司销售预期<ref name="HeartsPrepare" /><ref name="InnocenceSales">{{cite web | date = 2009-01-09 | script-title = ja:【ゲームソフト販売本数ランキング TOP30】 集計期間：2008年12月15日～12月21日 | url = http://www.famitsu.com/game/rank/top30/1221127_1134.html | publisher = ''[[Famitsu|Famitsu]]'' | language = ja | accessdate = 2012-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140819071156/http://www.famitsu.com/game/rank/top30/1221127_1134.html | archivedate = 2014-08-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《圣洁传说R》售周销量5.5万，次于当周的《[[装甲核心V|装甲核心V]]》和《[[生化危机_启示录|生化危机 启示录]]》，位居榜单第三<ref name="InnocenceFirstWeek">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/129414/Strong_debuts_for_Armored_Core_V_RE_Revelations_in_Japan.php | script-title = en:Strong debuts for Armored Core V Revelations in Japan | author = Caoili | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2012-02-01 | accessdate = 2015-02-07 | language = en }}</ref>。游戏在2012年7月时售出7.5万套，是当时第6畅销PlayStation Vita游戏<ref name="EuroVita">{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-07-18-how-is-ps-vita-doing-in-japan | script-title = en:How is PS Vita doing in Japan? | author = Yin-Poole | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | date = 2012-07-18 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | language = en }}</ref>。

《Fami通》对本作高多边形的人物模型、故事和角色表示称赞，认为作品总体而言迷人有趣。对于玩家可在战斗地图中自由移动，并能自由的定制角色这点，编辑也表示肯定。杂志批评了游戏一些小处，如难让新玩家上手、部分故事没有解释<ref name="FamReview">{{cite web | url = http://www.gemaga.com/2007/11/28/tales-of-innocence-ds-scores-high-gets-high-price | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence DS Scores High, Gets High Price | publisher = Gemaga.com | date = 2007-11-28 | accessdate = 2015-02-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110711083527/http://www.gemaga.com/2007/11/28/tales-of-innocence-ds-scores-high-gets-high-price | archivedate = 2011-07-11 | deadurl = yes | language = en }}</ref>。《圣洁传说》是当时系列中《Fami通》评分最高的游戏<ref name="CubedPreview" />。[[RPGamer|RPGamer]]的保罗·克勒在TGS 2007中对游戏印象很好，称游戏地图“流畅”，画面是“展会中DS最好的展示之一”<ref name="RPGpreview">{{cite web | url = http://www.rpgamer.com/event/tgs2007/impressions/toiimpression.html | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence - Tokyo Game Show Impression | author = Koehler, Paul | publisher = [[RPGamer|RPGamer]] | accessdate = 2015-02-09 | language = en | title = 存档副本 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210123836/http://www.rpgamer.com/event/tgs2007/impressions/toiimpression.html | archive-date = 2015-02-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。Cubed3的亚当·赖利实机试玩时给游戏总体好评，他称赞了游戏的配音量，还称游戏质量显得“异常之高”，是“系列迄今最完满的作品之一”。DS前作《暴风传说》在《圣洁传说》面前则“显得业余”<ref name="CubedPreview">{{cite web | url = http://www.cubed3.com/preview/257/1/tales-of-innocence-hands-on-nintendo-ds.html | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence (Hands-On) (Nintendo DS) Preview | author = Adam Riley | publisher = Cubed3 | date = 2008-01-13 | accessdate = 2015-02-09 | language = en}}</ref>。RPGFan的尼尔·德兰也和赖利一样称赞了游戏，表示游戏有迹成为“任天堂DS上的优质RPG，以及该高产RPG系列之中佳作”<ref name="RPGFpreview">{{cite web | url = http://www.rpgfan.com/previews/talesofinnocence/ | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence First Look Preview | author = Neal Chandran | publisher = RPGFan | date = 2007-07-12 | accessdate = 2015-02-09 | language = en }}</ref>。

《Fami通》亦给《圣洁传说R》好评。杂志赞赏了游戏升级的画面、重构的战斗系统，以及全新配音与故事<ref name="FamRReview">{{cite journal | author = | date = 2012-01-19 | script-title = ja:プレイステーションVita - テイルズオブイノセンスR | journal = [[Famitsu_Weekly|Famitsu Weekly]] | issue = 1205 | publisher = [[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]] | language = ja }}</ref>。日本网站Game Impress Watch高度评价游戏，网站在称赞新角色、升级的游戏系统和画面之时，也批评游戏部分地方略为繁难；文章总结称这是款“适合任何人”的角色扮演游戏<ref name="GWReview">{{cite web | url = http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/review/20120209_510662.html | script-title = ja:PS Vitaゲームレビュー / テイルズ オブ イノセンス R | publisher = Impress Watch | date = 2012-02-09 | accessdate = 2015-02-09 | language = ja}}</ref>。RPGFan的亚伯拉罕·阿什顿·刘称游戏瑕瑜互见。他对角色前生今世的反差、游戏的系统和配角表示称赞，但对主角表示不满。他还称游戏画面就Vita而言不佳，某些系统要素过时或难玩<ref name="RPGFvita">{{cite web | url = http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/Tales_of_Innocence_R/index.html | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence R Review | author = Liu, Abraham Ashton | publisher = RPGFan | date = 2012-03-05 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | language = en }}</ref>。在2013年3月颁布的《Fami通》2012年最佳游戏榜单中，《圣洁传说R》位列第13<ref name="NEreaders">{{cite web | url = http://nintendoeverything.com/famitsu-readers-rank-the-top-games-of-2012/ | script-title = en:Famitsu readers rank the top games of 2012 | author = Brian | publisher = Nintendo Everything | date = 2013-03-14 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | language = en }}</ref>。在日本网站Inside Games 2014年7月的榜单中，游戏跻身十大优秀Vita角色扮演游戏之列<ref name="InsideRankings">{{cite web | url = http://www.inside-games.jp/article/2014/07/23/78814.html | script-title = ja:「この夏、PS Vitaで遊びたい良作RPG」10選 | publisher = Inside Games | date = 2014-07-23 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | language = ja }}</ref>。

== 跨媒体 ==

公司在系列发行前后，推出了不同类型的宣传或补完作品。公司在宣传《圣洁传说》游戏时，制作了由多名前作角色演出的“声音冒险DVD”<ref name="InnocenceGuilds" />。一系列图书在游戏发行后推出，其中包括三册攻略本、[[金月龍之介|金月龍之介]]所著的两册小说（在2006年3月和2008年1月发行）、三卷“周刊圣洁传说”资料集（2007年11月至12月间发行）。攻略本收录有游戏指南、原话和制作者访谈<ref name="ToI Books">{{cite web | url = http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=78&category=1 | script-title = ja:テイルズ オブ イノセンス 関連商品 | publisher = [[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] | language = ja | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130317111715/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=78&category=1 | archivedate = 2013-03-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《[[Jump_Square|Jump Square]]》杂志在游戏发行前一个月，开始连载[[海童博行|海童博行]]作画的同名漫画<ref name="ToI manga">{{Cite web | date = 2007-11-16 | url = http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/cs/list/talesofinnocence/staffvoice/20071116.php | script-title = ja:11月16日（金） 「ジャンプSQ」 | work = バンダイナムコゲームス公式サイト | accessdate = 2012-11-20 | language = ja }}</ref>，该漫画后来分成三卷书籍出版<ref>{{cite web | url = http://books.shueisha.co.jp/CGI/search/zen_list.cgi?siries_isbn=X78-4-08-874491-9&siries_kanren_isbn=&mode=2 | script-title = ja:Tales　of　Innocence　−テイルズ　オブ　イノセンス− 全3巻 | publisher = Shueisha Inc. | accessdate = 2009-01-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090218155030/http://books.shueisha.co.jp/CGI/search/zen_list.cgi?siries_isbn=X78-4-08-874491-9&siries_kanren_isbn=&mode=2 | archivedate = 2009-02-18 | language = ja | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。此漫画和游戏的不同之处较多<ref name="ToI manga" />。改编[[广播剧|广播剧]]《圣洁传说 广播剧CD》共两话，分别于2008年6月25日和7月25日发行<ref name="ToI CDs">{{cite web | url = http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=78&category=2 | script-title = ja:テイルズ オブ イノセンス 関連商品 | publisher = [[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] | language = ja | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130317111725/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=78&category=2 | archivedate = 2013-03-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

万代南梦宫在《圣洁传说R》发行不久后，于2012年1月27日在[[iTunes|iTunes]]上，推出了开发的免费[[流動應用程式|流動應用程式]]。应用可播放《圣洁传说R》的部分歌曲，或展示游戏原画和角色档案。该应用中还有一款[[节奏游戏|节奏游戏]]，玩家可将得分发布在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上<ref name="ANNsmart">{{cite web | url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-02-20/tales-of-innocence-r-smartphone-app-plays-game-songs | script-title = en:Tales of Innocence R Smartphone App Plays Game's Songs | author = Sherman, Jennifer | publisher = [[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | date = 2012-02-20 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | language = en }}</ref>。《圣洁传说R》亦有改编漫画，其单行本《圣洁传说R 漫画集》于2012年5月25日发行<ref name="ToIR Books">{{cite web | url = http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=268&category=1 | script-title = ja:テイルズ オブ イノセンス 関連商品 | publisher = [[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] | language = ja | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130317110301/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=268&category=1 | archivedate = 2013-03-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

